Types:
- InitError, BadRequest, Throttled, Timeout, OOMKilled, Unhandled, Handled

HTTP:
- Invoke (sync): always 200 with payload; errors signaled by `X-Amz-Function-Error: Handled|Unhandled`
- Throttled: 429 on user API calls that cannot accept more invocations
- Bad input: 400; Not found: 404; Internal: 500 (control plane)

Error JSON shape:
{ "errorMessage": "...", "errorType": "Timeout|InitError|Unhandled|...", "stackTrace": ["..."] }